    <fr:title text="Hoeffding's Inequality">Hoeffding's Inequality</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Theorem</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
  Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X_1, \ldots , X_n]]></fr:tex> be independent centered <fr:link href="/002L/" title="Sub-Gaussian Random Variables" uri="https://kkanarios32.github.io/002L/" display-uri="002L" type="local">Sub-Gaussian Random Variables</fr:link>. Then for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a = (a_1, \ldots , a_n) \in  \mathbb {R}^n]]></fr:tex> and for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[t > 0]]></fr:tex>
  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\mathbb {P}\left (\left |\sum _{k = 1}^{n} a_j X_j\right | > t \right ) \leq  2 \exp \left (-c \frac {t^2}{\lVert  a\rVert ^2}\right )]]></fr:tex></html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
